ISLAMABAD, Mar 10 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Thursday that surprisingly there was no allegation of corruption against the Prime Minister in the no-confidence motion moved by the opposition.
In a tweet, he said that those who have moved no-trust motion and launched the movement are all corrupt.
